      <title>马尔代夫亲中国总统获得议会多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/maldives-pro-china-president-secures-majority-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫执政党人民全国大会党在周日举行的选举中赢得议会绝对多数席位，为总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖的亲华政策提供了推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/maldives-pro-china-president-secures-majority-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 05:32:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
