    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本的岸田在特别选举前的民意调查中陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/japan-s-kishida-struggles-in-polls-ahead-of-special-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄在华盛顿高调会见乔·拜登，但未能大幅提升民意支持率，这引发了人们对日本首相岸田文雄能否在选举中取得特别胜利的怀疑，而这可能是他长期担任领导人的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/japan-s-kishida-struggles-in-polls-ahead-of-special-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
